 src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔太updated    <br />\n估計依家d五毛人工應該高過普通d打工仔？</blockquote><br />\n收錢作評論<br />\n本質就係低端"},{"pid":"fc6064b2b2210f874ff526ec38cfc5a8bcd87812","tid":482121,"uid":53577,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">低端五毛點睇</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五毫+攞香港公屋綜援就唔低端啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36192c3c2d15ac3cf03ef6ae85c9530399c53f6","tid":482121,"uid":59898,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次有五毛狗出黎就貼果段佢嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b252fa6869b23021ba984a1ca97ebed1e7e67fce","tid":482121,"uid":80567,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/101032_ab26663e37e60e10c9fd139028495f6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F101032_ab26663e37e60e10c9fd139028495f6d.jpg&h=f81eafe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n低 端傳媒</blockquote><br />\n端係紅底資本 但好多高質學術文、政評"},{"pid":"3937c01e2d23dad4a1f567a48839243b6ba96402","tid":482121,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔離屋大掃除，啲蛇蟲鼠蟻咪逃走入自己屋企</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c394218c5d1a575114085e08c3908e2a773bb6a","tid":482121,"uid":23180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017